parameters.name: orgId
parameters.description: Organization numeric identifier. Append to list managed identities within an organization other than the requester's default.

parameters.name: search
parameters.description: Filter search parameter. Supports free text search on name and keywords: `platform:`.

parameters.name: max
parameters.description: Maximum number of results to return. Default: `20`.

parameters.name: offset
parameters.description: Number of results to skip for pagination. Default: `0`.
